cleanName: XY Trainer Kit Pikachu Libre and Suicune

extendedData.name: CardText
extendedData.value:
Featuring Pikachu Libre and the Water Legendary, Suicune. This Trainer Kit includes:

- Two 30-card decks, each with its own specially selected foil.
- Two guide books to teach you how to play the Pokemon TCG.
- A 2-player playmat that includes game tips and rules on the reverse side
- Damage counters and Special Condition markers
- A Pokemon designed game coin
- An illustrated deck box
- A code card for the Pokemon TCG Online
